"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381084","Department for Communities and Local Government","false","2015-06-18","<p>Government will consider any, and all, proposals for devolution of powers from cities, counties and towns that can demonstrate they have put in place strong and accountable governance arrangements. The most ambitious deals will devolve powers to directly elected metro mayors.</p>","Rayleigh and Wickford","Mr Mark Francois",,"2015-06-18T16:08:07.247Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381084/answer","Biography information for Mr Mark Francois","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381084/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381084/answer",,,,,"7","Communities and Local Government","Communities and Local Government","2015-06-15","Devolution: Urban Areas","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Communities and Local Government, with reference to the Chancellor of the Exchequer's speech on 14 May 2015, whether devolution of certain powers and resources to city-regions is contingent on cities accepting a mayoral model of governance.","false","Biography information for Emma Reynolds","Wolverhampton North East","Emma Reynolds","2488"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381085","Department for Communities and Local Government","false","2015-06-23","<p>Through the Local Government Transparency Code we require all councils to be more transparent about the value of their social housing stock.<br><br>The Department will outline our proposals for the Housing Bill when it is published.</p>","Great Yarmouth","Brandon Lewis","2514","2015-06-23T12:20:43.317Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381085/answer","Biography information for Brandon Lewis","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381085/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/381085/answer",,,,,"7","Communities and Local Government","Communities and Local Government","2015-06-15","Council Housing: Empty Property","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Communities and Local Government, pursuant to the Answer of 8 June 2015 to Question 1079, if the Government will make an estimate of the vacancy rates of high-value council homes.","false","Biography information for Emma Reynolds","Wolverhampton North East","Emma Reynolds","2513"
